<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-center mb-5">About Puzzler23</h1>
            
            <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap me-2 text-primary"></i>College Induction Program</h3>
                    <p>Puzzler23 is designed specifically for college induction programs to help new students:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Break the ice and interact with peers</li>
                        <li>Exercise their problem-solving skills</li>
                        <li>Have fun while learning</li>
                        <li>Build confidence in a friendly environment</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="card h-100">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-puzzle-piece me-2 text-primary"></i>Puzzler Game</h4>
                            <p>Traditional riddle-solving game where you earn points for correct answers. Perfect for testing your knowledge and logical thinking.</p>
                            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                <li><i class="fas fa-check text-success me-2"></i>Correct answers = Points</li>
                                <li><i class="fas fa-check text-success me-2"></i>Various difficulty levels</li>
                                <li><i class="fas fa-check text-success me-2"></i>Instant feedback</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="card h-100">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-times-circle me-2 text-warning"></i>Wrong Answer Only</h4>
                            <p>A unique twist where you get points for wrong answers! Encourages creative thinking and helps students relax about being "wrong."</p>
                            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                <li><i class="fas fa-times text-warning me-2"></i>Wrong answers = Points</li>
                                <li><i class="fas fa-times text-warning me-2"></i>Creative thinking encouraged</li>
                                <li><i class="fas fa-times text-warning me-2"></i>No pressure to be right</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

